  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A single-center registry to prospectively evaluate the safety of non-cardiac/non-thoracic
      magnetic resonance imaging (MRI) in patients with implanted cardiac devices (pacemakers and
      implantable cardioverter defibrillators).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Evaluation of safety of MR scanning of patients with implanted cardiac devices. Device
      parameters pre and post MR imaging will be assessed.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
